{"id":232409479,"title":"【寶可夢劍盾】數位板已經上架囉 ><","content":"http://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9.jpg\n《寶可夢 劍盾》即將在任天堂 Switch 平台登陸了。目前日本 Switch 的 eShop 已經正式上架了這款遊戲的商品頁面，從而曝光了遊戲的最終容量大小和支援的相關配備資訊。 \n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/PVq8Kpb.png\n 此次《寶可夢 劍盾》的容量大小為 9.5 GB 且支援 Switch Pro，目前日本的 eShop 上已經可以進行遊戲的預載了。而香港任天堂的官網也開啟預購了，預購玩家可以預載，想要第一時間玩到的朋友不要錯過。 \n\n本來一直很擔心會跟皮伊版一樣強制用joy-con玩，現在終於放下心中的一顆大石頭了，只可惜確定不支援雲端備份存檔，只能平常多做點好事希望主機不要無預警壞掉了QQ\n\n文章來源：\n https://game.kikinote.net/12358","excerpt":"《寶可夢 劍盾》即將在任天堂 Switch 平台登陸了。目前日本 Switch 的 eShop 已經正式上架了這款遊戲的商品頁面，從而曝光了遊戲的最終容量大小和支援的相關配備資訊。此次《寶可夢 劍盾》","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"99049f5e-bb3d-420f-b708-52c384359952","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-31T07:12:15.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-31T07:12:15.356Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":10,"tags":[],"topics":["寶可夢劍盾","寶可夢"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"寶可夢","forumAlias":"pokemon","school":"中臺科技大學","department":"資訊管理系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":10}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9.jpg"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/PVq8Kpb.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7940f1f2-5b4d-44c1-8a64-161970c3faa3","url":"https://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9l.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9l.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9l.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-31T07:12:15.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-31T07:12:15.356Z"},{"id":"7940f1f2-5b4d-44c1-8a64-161970c3faa3","url":"http://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/WQZNFm9","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/WQZNFm9l.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-31T07:12:15.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-3